radish_love.description: A love poem for Cen about radishes

alex_dog_mess.description: A webpage telling Alex to clean up

droid-union.description: A Star Wars themed labor politics advocacy site celebrating droid worker rights and unionization, with interactive visuals inspired by the Phantom Menace including Trade Federation aesthetics, battle droid solidarity, and worker empowerment messaging

rat_bushwick.description: A humorous guide to things to do in Bushwick for a hungry rat, featuring funny rat visualizations, ASCII art, and pixel animations. Includes rat-themed activities like dumpster diving, pizza rat expeditions, bodega raids, and more with interactive elements and retro arcade styling.

bushwick_run_map.description: Interactive map of Cen's running route around Bushwick with distance tracking, elevation data, pace information, and route visualization. Features a leaflet map with the route path, markers for start/end points and notable locations, distance breakdown by segment, and running stats.

leaflet.description: embed leaflet functionality in running map

cen_veggie_haul.description: Interactive visualization of Cen's veggie haul from the farmer's market - greenbeans, radishes, celery, daikon, three potatoes, ginger, green onion, garlic for $22. Shows each veggie with icons and pricing breakdown.
